original_title: Nanci Griffith: Other Voices, Other Rooms
overview: Nanci Griffith performs her Grammy Award winning album "Other Voices, Other Rooms" live at Paramount Theater in Austin, Texas on April 28th, 1993 with special guests including Emmylou Harris, Bob Dylan, Townes Van Zandt, Odetta, John Prine, Guy Clark, Iris DeMent, and many more.
title: Nanci Griffith: Other Voices, Other Rooms
